Direct Known Subclasses:
Region.RegionBorderCache
public abstract class BorderCache<T extends Region<T>> extends com.telenav.kivakit.component.BaseComponent
There should be no need for end-users of MesaKit to use BorderCache objects since they are an implementation detail of different Regions to provide containment testing via Region.contains(Location), as well as other such tests.

Loads PBF border data for regions and converts it to an indexed form, BorderSpatialIndex, that can be rapidly queried. The border data can be found in the mesakit-assets project under the folder "boundaries". The borders can be loaded with loadBorders() and region codes associated with the borders with loadIdentities(). The borders themselves can be retrieved with borders(Region).

Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
